article.description: — Shavar Reynolds Jr. scored a career-high 25 points as Monmouth topped Saint Joseph's 87-75 on Saturday. Marcus McClary added 24 points for Monmouth. McClary also had seven rebounds.
article.headline: Reynolds Jr. leads Monmouth over Saint Joseph's 87-75
article.linkText: Reynolds Jr. leads Monmouth over Saint Joseph's 87-75
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Shavar Reynolds Jr. scored a career-high 25 points as Monmouth topped Saint Joseph's 87-75 on Saturday. Marcus McClary added 24 points for Monmouth. McClary also had seven rebounds. George Papas had 18 points and six rebounds for Monmouth (3-1). Walker Miller added 15 points and 12 rebounds. Jordan Hall scored a career-high 24 points and had 10 rebounds and five assists for Saint Joseph's (2-2). Taylor Funk added 16 points. Erik Reynolds II had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
